<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[اجتزم]</span> النخل: إِذا خَرَصه <span class="c2">«٢»</span>، قال <span class="c2">«٣»</span>:<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>... .. كالنَّخْلِ طافَ بِهِ المُجْتَزِمْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
